- Thanks.

416
00:26:57,459 --> 00:26:59,220
- And this. Try this too.
- That's enough. Thanks.

417
00:26:59,220 --> 00:27:01,880
That's more than enough.
Is it a bit inappropriate

418
00:27:02,680 --> 00:27:03,819
