470
00:31:05,824 --> 00:31:06,912
Do you have a boyfriend?

471
00:31:11,519 --> 00:31:14,039
Liu Qianqian, do you have a boyfriend?

472
00:31:14,559 --> 00:31:17,920
I … like… you!

473
00:31:19,599 --> 00:31:21,079
